      "content": "honestly im just sitting here in this cafe in bali and it hit me how much of a ghost i am. like i wander around these places and i don't actually exist to anyone here. if i just stopped showing up tomorrow... i dont think anyone would even notice a gap. it feels like my life is just zero sum. i take up space but i don't actually add anything.",
